{"tid":1424741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共匪已發動各鄉下港民鬥","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:03:34.000Z","uid":279702,"like":41,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"efa49fa14d6819f364456695ed17667d551d073f","tid":1424741,"uid":279702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:27:16.000Z","msg":"我係P牌狗，我係福建出生香港長大既福建HI<br />\n但屌你老母<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我係香港人</span></strong><br />\n我琴日仲叫人正名福建幫係黑社會<br />\n唔撚好屌福建人<br />\n<br />\n但原來我岩岩先知<br />\n我鄉下成班親戚既福建group真係吹雞<br />\n仲要係唔使有證就可以坐洗頭艇落黎<br />\n屌佢地老母。<br />\n利申我無微信，係我老母話我知<br />\n我勁驚佢係微信同鄉下親戚講我有發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆咁即係唔撚止福建啦<br />\n大家諗定到時係街度<br />\n見到自己同鄉揸刀都唔撚使理<br />\n屌佢老母打大力啲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後最撚灰係....<br />\n班親戚話要落黎斬人，<br />\n屌你咁落黎第一個斬我囉好無。"},{"pid":"9626dfba36bb9cdd0148b3880b50a3fec3461124","tid":1424741,"uid":279702,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推<br />\n屌，共匪已發動民鬥</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"815c9e2cc8645d73d0898a899a7c5b56a6cd7f58","tid":1424741,"uid":54721,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"你自己清理門戶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fbe092863e143bd5bccd207b528bc28281be41","tid":1424741,"uid":4964,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"洗頭艇如果有證據,又係輿論核彈<br />\n入境處同水警嚴重失職兼有可疑"},{"pid":"523c24e64a254a988f69fdb14b0870374955f3bb","tid":1424741,"uid":279702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:30:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-larg